    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Chess Programming Wiki</b> is a repository of information about <a href=\"/Programming\" title=\"Programming\">programming</a> computers to play <a href=\"/Chess\" title=\"Chess\">chess</a>. Our goal is to provide a reference for every aspect of chess programming, information about <a href=\"/Category:Programmer\" title=\"Category:Programmer\">programmers</a>, <a href=\"/Category:Researcher\" title=\"Category:Researcher\">researcher</a> and <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">engines</a>. You'll find different ways to implement <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">LMR</a> and <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">bitboard</a> stuff like <a href=\"/Best_Magics_so_far\" title=\"Best Magics so far\">best magics</a> for most dense <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">magic bitboard</a> tables. For didactic purposes, the <a href=\"/CPW-Engine\" title=\"CPW-Engine\">CPW-Engine</a> has been developed by some wiki members. You can start browsing using the left-hand navigation bar. All of our content is arranged hierarchically, so you can see every page by following just those links. If you are looking for a specific page or catchword you can use the search box on top.\n</p><p>CPW was founded by <a href=\"/Mark_Lefler\" title=\"Mark Lefler\">Mark Lefler</a> on October 26, 2007 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, first hosted on <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikispaces\">Wikispaces</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Due to that site closure <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, it moved to its present new host at <b>www.chessprogramming.org</b>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Hot_Topics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Hot Topics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Basics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Basics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Principal_Topics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Principal Topics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forums_.26_Discord_Channels\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forums &amp; Discord Channels</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Lists\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lists</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Miscellaneous\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Miscellaneous</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Statistics\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Statistics</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Thanks\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Thanks</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">9</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hot_Topics\">Hot Topics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Hot Topics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Topics people search/discuss much\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Leela Chess Zero</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Basics\">Basics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Basics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Getting_Started\" title=\"Getting Started\">Getting Started</a> - if you are new to chess programming</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Principal_Topics\">Principal Topics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Principal Topics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chess\" title=\"Chess\">Chess</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Programming\" title=\"Programming\">Programming</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">Artificial Intelligence</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Knowledge\" title=\"Knowledge\">Knowledge</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">Learning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">User Interface</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">Protocols</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forums_.26_Discord_Channels\">Forums &amp; Discord Channels</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forums &amp; Discord Channels\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Computer Chess Forums</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Discord_Channels\" title=\"Discord Channels\">Discord Channels</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lists\">Lists</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Lists\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Cartoons\" title=\"Cartoons\">Cartoons</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Dictionary\" title=\"Dictionary\">Dictionary</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> including the <a href=\"/CPW-Engine\" title=\"CPW-Engine\">CPW-Engine</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Dedicated_Chess_Computers\" title=\"Dedicated Chess Computers\">Dedicated Chess Computers</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Engine_Releases\" title=\"Engine Releases\">Engine Releases</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Games\" title=\"Games\">Games</a>, some other <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">AI</a>-Games, where computer chess may borrow some ideas </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hardware\" title=\"Hardware\">Hardware</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History\" title=\"History\">History</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Periodical\" title=\"Periodical\">Periodical</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tournaments_and_Matches\" title=\"Tournaments and Matches\">Tournaments and Matches</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Miscellaneous\">Miscellaneous</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Miscellaneous\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Acknowledgments\" title=\"Acknowledgments\">Acknowledgments</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Recommended_Reading\" title=\"Recommended Reading\">Recommended Reading</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Statistics\">Statistics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Statistics\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> Articles: 4,269</li>\n<li> Pages: 8,026</li>\n<li> Files: 2,969</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Thanks\">Thanks</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Thanks\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Thanks for visiting our site!\nWe hope you like the work we have done.\n</p><p><a href=\"/Mark_Lefler\" title=\"Mark Lefler\">Mark Lefler</a> and the rest of the CPW team.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Main_Page&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=17344&amp;start=4\">Re: community test result web page?</a> by <a href=\"/Mark_Lefler\" title=\"Mark Lefler\">Mark Lefler</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2007</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20180216204915/http://chessprogramming.wikispaces.com/\">Wikispaces Chessprogramming - home</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, February 16, 2018)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66573\">Chess Programming Wiki</a> by <a href=\"/Jon_Dart\" title=\"Jon Dart\">Jon Dart</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 12, 2018</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301081813\nCache expiry: 3600\nDynamic content: true\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.018 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 90/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 178/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 15/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:1-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301081813 and revision id 27057\n -->\n"
